newsitem.title: MALAYSIA: Malaysia rubber quiet, MRELB prices unavailable.
newsitem.headline: Malaysia rubber quiet, MRELB prices unavailable.

text.p: Malaysian rubber market was quiet with prices quoted by dealers little changed from Wednesday's close.
There were no prices available from the Malaysian Rubber Exchange and Licensing Board following a power breakdown at the exchange, dealers said.
Dealers said SMR CV was offered at 375 cents, SMR L at 354, SMR 5 at 325, SMR 10 at 313, SMR 20 at 312 and drum latex at 245-250.
There were very few enquiries from Asian and European buyers who have not been active in the market.
